enum icmpstr::IRegistryConsistInfo::QueryFlags

Enumerator:
QF_NONE 
QF_ANY_INTERFACE  Supporting of any specified interfaces is enough to interprete component as compatible one.
QF_INCLUDE_UNDEFINED  If active, all undefined (without available meta information) elements will be also included.
